15225 #if FF_CODE_PAGE != 0 && FF_CODE_PAGE < 900
15226 WCHAR ff_uni2oem ( /* Returns OEM code character, zero on error */
15227  DWORD uni, /* UTF-16 encoded character to be converted */
15228  WORD cp /* Code page for the conversion */
15229 )
15230 {
15231  WCHAR c = 0;
15232  const WCHAR *p = CVTBL(uc, FF_CODE_PAGE);
15233 
15234 
15235  if (uni < 0x80) { /* ASCII? */
15236  c = (WCHAR)uni;
15237 
15238  } else { /* Non-ASCII */
15239  if (uni < 0x10000 && cp == FF_CODE_PAGE) { /* Is it in BMP and valid code page? */
15240  for (c = 0; c < 0x80 && uni != p[c]; c++) ;
15241  c = (c + 0x80) & 0xFF;
15242  }
15243  }
15244 
15245  return c;
15246 }

15255 
15256 
15257  if (oem < 0x80) { /* ASCII? */
15258  c = oem;
15259 
15260  } else { /* Extended char */
15261  if (cp == FF_CODE_PAGE) { /* Is it a valid code page? */
15262  if (oem < 0x100) c = p[oem - 0x80];
15263  }
15264  }

15278 #if FF_CODE_PAGE >= 900
15279 WCHAR ff_uni2oem ( /* Returns OEM code character, zero on error */
15280  DWORD uni, /* UTF-16 encoded character to be converted */
15281  WORD cp /* Code page for the conversion */
15282 )
15283 {
15284  const WCHAR *p;
15285  WCHAR c = 0, uc;
15286  UINT i = 0, n, li, hi;
15287 
15288 
15289  if (uni < 0x80) { /* ASCII? */
15290  c = (WCHAR)uni;
15291 
15292  } else { /* Non-ASCII */
15293  if (uni < 0x10000 && cp == FF_CODE_PAGE) { /* Is it in BMP and valid code page? */
15294  uc = (WCHAR)uni;
15295  p = CVTBL(uni2oem, FF_CODE_PAGE);
15296  hi = sizeof CVTBL(uni2oem, FF_CODE_PAGE) / 4 - 1;
15297  li = 0;
15298  for (n = 16; n; n--) {
15299  i = li + (hi - li) / 2;
15300  if (uc == p[i * 2]) break;
15301  if (uc > p[i * 2]) {
15302  li = i;
15303  } else {
15304  hi = i;
15305  }
15306  }
15307  if (n != 0) c = p[i * 2 + 1];
15308  }
15309  }
15310 
15311  return c;
15312 }

15362 WCHAR ff_uni2oem ( /* Returns OEM code character, zero on error */
15363  DWORD uni, /* UTF-16 encoded character to be converted */
15364  WORD cp /* Code page for the conversion */
15365 )
15366 {
15367  const WCHAR *p;
15368  WCHAR c = 0, uc;
15369  UINT i, n, li, hi;
15370 
15371 
15372  if (uni < 0x80) { /* ASCII? */
15373  c = (WCHAR)uni;
15374 
15375  } else { /* Non-ASCII */
15376  if (uni < 0x10000) { /* Is it in BMP? */
15377  uc = (WCHAR)uni;
15378  p = 0;
15379  if (cp < 900) { /* SBCS */
15380  for (i = 0; cp_code[i] != 0 && cp_code[i] != cp; i++) ; /* Get conversion table */
15381  p = cp_table[i];
15382  if (p) { /* Is it valid code page ? */
15383  for (c = 0; c < 0x80 && uc != p[c]; c++) ; /* Find OEM code in the table */
15384  c = (c + 0x80) & 0xFF;
15385  }
15386  } else { /* DBCS */
15387  switch (cp) { /* Get conversion table */
15388  case 932 : p = uni2oem932; hi = sizeof uni2oem932 / 4 - 1; break;
15389  case 936 : p = uni2oem936; hi = sizeof uni2oem936 / 4 - 1; break;
15390  case 949 : p = uni2oem949; hi = sizeof uni2oem949 / 4 - 1; break;
15391  case 950 : p = uni2oem950; hi = sizeof uni2oem950 / 4 - 1; break;
15392  }
15393  if (p) { /* Is it valid code page? */
15394  li = 0;
15395  for (n = 16; n; n--) { /* Find OEM code */
15396  i = li + (hi - li) / 2;
15397  if (uc == p[i * 2]) break;
15398  if (uc > p[i * 2]) {
15399  li = i;
15400  } else {
15401  hi = i;
15402  }
15403  }
15404  if (n != 0) c = p[i * 2 + 1];
15405  }
15406  }
15407  }
15408  }
15409 
15410  return c;
15411 }

15414 WCHAR ff_oem2uni ( /* Returns Unicode character, zero on error */
15415  WCHAR oem, /* OEM code to be converted (DBC if >=0x100) */
15416  WORD cp /* Code page for the conversion */
15417 )
15418 {
15419  const WCHAR *p;
15420  WCHAR c = 0;
15421  UINT i, n, li, hi;
15422 
15423 
15424  if (oem < 0x80) { /* ASCII? */
15425  c = oem;
15426 
15427  } else { /* Extended char */
15428  p = 0;
15429  if (cp < 900) { /* SBCS */
15430  for (i = 0; cp_code[i] != 0 && cp_code[i] != cp; i++) ; /* Get table */
15431  p = cp_table[i];
15432  if (p) { /* Is it a valid CP ? */
15433  if (oem < 0x100) c = p[oem - 0x80];
15434  }
15435  } else { /* DBCS */
15436  switch (cp) {
15437  case 932 : p = oem2uni932; hi = sizeof oem2uni932 / 4 - 1; break;
15438  case 936 : p = oem2uni936; hi = sizeof oem2uni936 / 4 - 1; break;
15439  case 949 : p = oem2uni949; hi = sizeof oem2uni949 / 4 - 1; break;
15440  case 950 : p = oem2uni950; hi = sizeof oem2uni950 / 4 - 1; break;
15441  }
15442  if (p) {
15443  li = 0;
15444  for (n = 16; n; n--) {
15445  i = li + (hi - li) / 2;
15446  if (oem == p[i * 2]) break;
15447  if (oem > p[i * 2]) {
15448  li = i;
15449  } else {
15450  hi = i;
15451  }
15452  }
15453  if (n != 0) c = p[i * 2 + 1];
15454  }
15455  }
15456  }
15457 
15458  return c;
15459 }
